    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality masterpiece. This vehicle has been curated for the most discerning collector, maintained to an exacting standard that defies its age. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, every detail radiates a level of care and preservation seldom seen on the market. This is more than a pre-owned vehicle; it is an investment-grade example of automotive excellence, offering an uncompromising driving experience for those who settle for nothing less than the best.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
