    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it's time for her to find a new home. This car has been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away and pampered like a member of the family. She looks and drives like she just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014honestly, you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish on her. She\u2019s smooth, powerful, and ready for your next weekend adventure. I\u2019ve taken care of all the little details so you can just turn the key and enjoy the ride. Come by for a coffee and a chat, and see for yourself why I'm so in love with this car!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is a surgically maintained specimen for the discerning driver who understands the value of a perfectly indexed valvetrain and optimized thermal management. We\u2019re looking at a zero-compromise build with a chassis that exhibits unparalleled torsional rigidity. The power delivery is exceptionally linear, thanks to a precision-calibrated ECU map that maximizes the efficiency of the forced induction system. Every bushing has been inspected for zero deflection, and the unsprung weight has been minimized via lightweight forged alloys to ensure the suspension geometry remains undisturbed under high lateral G-loads. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a masterclass in automotive engineering, preserved in a state that puts factory-fresh units to shame. Fluids are flushed religiously with high-temp synthetics, and the compression ratios across all cylinders are within negligible tolerances. Dialed-in and ready for the apex.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Flawless condition. Zero issues. Showroom quality. Lowest price on the market. Won't last.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
