    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine yourself behind the wheel of a true automotive masterpiece, a time capsule that defies the passage of years. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a symphony of polished chrome and whisper-quiet engineering. Every curve of its flawless bodywork tells a story of meticulous care and weekend escapes where the road never ended. Sliding into the cabin is like stepping into a private sanctuary, where the scent of rich leather and the tactile click of every dial reminds you of an era when things were built to be cherished. This is a rare opportunity to own a legend that looks and feels as though it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014a pristine companion ready for your next grand adventure.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
