    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this meticulously curated masterpiece. This vehicle presents in true showroom condition, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic excellence. For the buyer who demands nothing less than the absolute best, this represents a rare opportunity to own a vehicle of peerless quality and documented care.",
      "price": 48900.0,
