      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! It truly breaks my heart to see this absolute beauty go, but it's time for her to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as cherished. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014honestly, she looks like she just rolled off the showroom floor! Every curve is polished to perfection, and the drive is as smooth as silk. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, you\u2019ve found it. Come by for a coffee and a chat, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of your dream car!",
      "price": 44500.0,
