    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a pinnacle-spec E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 power plant with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a fully bulletproofed VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring total structural integrity under high-lateral G-loads. The individual throttle bodies are perfectly synchronized, delivering instantaneous transient response. The chassis has been dialed in with a corner-balanced Bilstein B16 coilover setup, and the Getrag 6-speed shifts with bolt-action precision. This is a concourse-grade driver\u2019s machine with impeccable paint depth and a cabin that retains its factory Nappa leather scent. Zero deferred maintenance\u2014just pure, high-compression mechanical bliss.",
